msContents.summary: Adaptation into Persian of an Oral system of teaching living languages. The original is for teaching French. This adaptation is for teaching or learning Persian using the same system and the same vocabulary as the French. The first 30 lessons show both Persian and English translations. The second 30 lessons are lists of Persian words with no translations. The translator's name is Romanized several different ways on the title pages.
